author: PlayStation
description:
Start your engines — the Pups are back and ready to race! 🚗💨
Get the whole family in on the fun with PAW Patrol Rescue Wheels: Championship! Choose your child’s favorite Pup (or even a playful villain!) and race through Adventure Bay, Foggy Bottom, and the Jungle.
Kids can perform exciting stunts, drift around the track, and use each Pup’s unique power-up to chase down victory — all in a safe, family-friendly racing game. 🏆🎮
Play solo or enjoy split-screen co-op for even more fun with friends and family! 🐾
Buckle up & get ready for a PAWsome race!
